cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with visual object tracking using correlation filters and convolutional features. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper focuses on unmanned aerial vehicles (UAV) and their ability to perform object following. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a novel tracker with online enhanced background learning. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with developing a more accurate appearance model for object tracking. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with visual object tracking using convolutional features.
